<h3 id="contributions">contributions</h3>
<blockquote>
  <p>We present a novel neural dialog model adapted from conditional variational autoencoders  which introduces a latent variable that can capture discourse-level variations as described above<br />
We propose Knowledge-Guided CVAE which enables easy integration of expert
knowledge and results in performance improvement and model interpretability.</p>
</blockquote>
